          <h3>Rey Za Burrel</h3>
          <img class="ce_pic_square" src="image/Rey.png" alt="Rey.png">
          <p>Rey Za Burrel (レイ・ザ・バレル Rei Za Bareru) is a character that appears in the Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Destiny television series.</p>
          <p>Rey is a quiet, calm, and polite soldier who keeps himself out of other people's way; he gladly follows his orders with stoic efficiency. He shows extreme loyalty to the Chairman of the PLANTs, Gilbert Durandal.</p>
          <p>Rey is an ace pilot of ZAFT. Rey is capable enough to stand against Neo Roanoke in his Exus, while also destroying two of the Exus's four gunbarrels. After switching to the ZGMF-X666S Legend, he was also able to single-handedly fight and destroy at least one of the massive GFAS-X1 Destroy mobile suits. Able to maintain coolness in tough battles along with good situation analysis, Rey often assumes a leadership role to help keep a more hot-blooded Shinn calm while creating openings for his partner to attack. Apart from his skills as a pilot, Rey has been shown to be an adept piano player.</p>

