          <p>Performance wise, the suit is superior to the Second Stage Series and is comparable to that of the Strike Freedom Gundam as seen during their battle. Like the Destiny Gundam, the Legend Gundam is armored with Variable Phase Shift Armor and powered by the new Hyper-Deuterion Engine, granting it sufficient energy to power its energy-intensive weaponry and systems. It also possesses full atmospheric-flight capabilities.</p>

